# .tool-versions — version manifest for asdf, mise, and similar tools
#
# Adopted in P3.7 of Phase 3 (environment hardening).
#
# Reference: https://asdf-vm.com / https://mise.jdx.dev
#
# Versions sourced from canonical project files:
# - golang: go.work
# - rust: tools/raccoon-cli/rust-toolchain.toml
# - golangci-lint: pinned at v2.12.2 in .github/workflows/ci.yml
#   (golangci-lint-action@v6 with explicit `version: v2.12.2`) AND
#   the v2.x major series is pinned in .golangci.yml (`version: "2"`).
#   Keep this manifest in sync with the CI pin.
#
# Install via asdf:
#   asdf install
#
# Or via mise (recommended modern alternative):
#   mise install
#
# Tools without asdf/mise plugin (lefthook, shellcheck) install separately:
#   brew install lefthook shellcheck
#   or
#   go install github.com/evilmartians/lefthook@latest

golang 1.25.7
rust 1.90.0
golangci-lint 2.12.2
